    "## Review Analysis\n",
    "\n",
    "The ReviewAnalyzer class is used to analyze a collection of simplified Glassdoor reviews stored in a DataFrame. The ReviewAnalyzer class works with the full set of simplified reviews to calculate useful summary information.\n",
    "Using this class, we can count the number of reviews, calculate average ratings, generate descriptive statistics, group reviews by selected categories, and create rating buckets such as low, medium, and high. Because the complete Glassdoor dataset contains over 8 million reviews, this demonstration uses only the first 50 rows to show how the analysis methods work on a smaller sample."
   ]
